['4', "I watched this on the tv 'back in the day' and hadn't seen it since. Luckily (for me) a friend reminded me of the title and that enabled me to track it down. Given that I love anything with Pirates in it this was bound to be a winner. Could be improved by better plot 'pacing' but ultimately rip-roaring fun throughout. Brian Blessed is made for the part Ben Gunn is suitably deranged but for me the show is stolen by Nick Brimble as 'Keelhaul' one of the great villains of our time.", [1, 0, 0, 5, 23], [0, 0, 8, 52, 57]]